Black land " seed”out of agricultural modernization-Xinhua
Xinhua News Agency, Harbin, July 26th topic: Black land“seed”out of agricultural modernization
In the middle of summer, two spray-spraying aircraft passed from the 10,000 acres of high-yield demonstration field in the second operation station of the fifth management area of Friendship Farm, forming two white lines. The words“the first field in the world”, which were planted with black rice seedlings, were particularly striking in the green fields.
Kong Lingqiang, the station chief, said the aircraft can spray agents on more than 6,000 acres of arable land a day, about eight times the efficiency of drones and hundreds of times the efficiency of artificial.
This farm is located in Youyi County, Heilongjiang Province, the first grain-producing province in China. From the sound of cutting rice in the past to the sound of rumbling motors today, traditional Chinese farming and farms have transformed in this black soil belt.
In addition to aircraft, satellites are also used in the modern agricultural production of Friendship Farm.
On the one hand, they use satellite remote sensing technology to achieve accurate fertilization, reduce agricultural input, reduce pollution;on the other hand, satellite navigation technology can improve the standard operation level of agricultural machinery in the field.
In this year's rice production process, the farm will be satellite navigation unmanned rice planting technology operating area expanded from 3,000 acres last year to 30,000 acres.
This technology makes seedling planting more uniform,can maximize the use of sunlight and arable land resources, and can save 16 yuan per acre of labor costs.
The farm tries new technologies such as informationization and intelligence in agricultural production, forming the largest group of agricultural machinery in our country from the ground to the sky.
According to statistics, at present, the total amount of farm machinery is 49,000 units (pieces), and the comprehensive mechanization rate of the field is 99.8%.
Agricultural machinery operation to achieve GPS satellite navigation 100%, dry field precision sowing 100%,dry field high-power locomotive operation 100%.
"Green agriculture, smart agriculture, digital agriculture is the direction of agricultural modernization .”
Friendship Farm director Liu Hua Lian said.
The key to agricultural modernization lies in scientific and technological progress.
In recent years, Heilongjiang Agricultural reclamation, represented by farms, has played a demonstration and leading role in modern agricultural“aircraft carrier”, and has initially established a modern agricultural industry system dominated by large-scale planting, standardized production and industrial management.
On the outskirts of Friendship County, there is an agricultural machinery Expo park covering an area of 350,000 square meters.
Here, more than 140 sets of agricultural machinery (pieces) introduced and used by Heilongjiang agricultural reclamation over the years are displayed.
These agricultural tools and farms have witnessed the development of China's agricultural modernization.
She Xiaojia for everyone -- Hefei, Anhui Jiangkou River Lianwei mass transfer direct hit-Xinhua Net
Xinhua News Agency, Hefei, July 26th: She Xiaojia for everyone — The mass transfer of Jiangkou River Lianwei in Hefei, Anhui Province
Xinhua News Agency reporter Chen Shangying, Wang Liwu, Liu Xiacun
On July 25, more than 4 pm, Fu Kunbao wearing mud-covered rubber shoes,from the front room to the back room,and his wife Zhou Yan back and forth busy packing things.
"I received a call from the village cadres to transfer, and I was still collecting grass in the field."”
Fu Kunbao said that he has transferred more than 60 acres of land, planted rice, now growing well, “ yesterday also hit the medicine, tools and nothing to pick up."”
Fu Kunbao pointed to the pesticide sprayer placed in the corner, " No one wants to be flooded at home,give up a small home for everyone."”
In response to the continued high water pressure and possible heavy rainfall in Chaohu, the city of Hefei, Anhui Province, is preparing to open the Jiangkou River, where Fu Kunbao's family is located, on the 26th to divert water storage.
Jiangkou River Lian Wei is located in Feixi County, adjacent to the Chaohu embankment.
There are thousands of villagers involved in Yandian Township and Sanhe town in the polder that need to be transferred.
As of 16: 00 on the 25th, the water level of Chaohu Lake, China's fifth largest freshwater lake, remains at a high level of 13.2 meters, exceeding the guaranteed water level of 0.7 meters.
Fu Kunbao's kitchen is clean,with a pot of pumpkin head vegetables on the table,eggs and some stewed vegetables in the fridge.
"Did not expect to move, Jiangkou River water is now looking good." ”
Zhou Yan said that the home is a bungalow, some large objects have not yet figured out where to put.
"Pack up your valuables first,refrigerators and televisions, which can be temporarily placed in high-rise neighbors or relatives."”
Wang Liwen, a village cadre, gave Fu Kunbao an idea.
Wang Liwen is responsible for the transfer and placement of 13 villagers, one family by family notification, confirm the resettlement plan for each person.
The nearest settlement from Fu Kunbao home is Yandian Xiang Su Xiaoxiao School, about 2 kilometers away.
In addition to the large size, Fu Kunbao and his family have a headache with more than 1000 pounds of food and some new furniture.
"The grain is ready to be dragged to relatives' homes,and the furniture can't be moved.”
As soon as the couple discussed it, they put a stool under the newly bought bed and raised it about half a meter high.
At 6 p.m., Fu Kunbao began to use a tricycle to transport things to relatives, and Zhou Yan continued to pack at home.
More than 11 p.m., the couple looked back and forth at home, pulled on the switch, ready to go to the placement point.
"I hope the water will return early.”
Said Fu Kunbao.
At 9: 30 a.m. on July 26, the reporter saw at the scene of Jiangkou River Lian Wei, the local area has been ready to divide the flood before the preparation.
