Xinhua News Agency, Moscow, July 25, according to the Russian Ministry of Defense plans, the upgraded version of the Russian gunship (hereinafter referred to as Wuzhi) card-52 --card-52M will be completed for the first time in December this year, the model in reconnaissance, communications and weapons performance will be greatly improved.
According to the Russian "Izvestia" recently reported that Wuzhika-52M named "super alligator“, its development contract was signed by the Russian military and military units in April last year, the first batch of two of the upgraded version of Wuzhika is in the Russian”progress" aerospace group company's Far East helicopter factory to undergo transformation, its national testing and improvement of the finishing work will end before October 2022.
