The Yellow River, which aroused the pride of countless literati, gave birth to the beautiful and rich Ningxia Plain. Now, Ningxia, which has the reputation of“plugging the Jiangnan”, is adhering to the concept of“ecological priority and green development”and pursuing the poetic“Yellow River Dream”.
The“Blue Wave Dream " of the River Shimizu Show”
The Yellow River flows through Ningxia 397 kilometers and is the“mother River”that nurtures one side.
However, with the rapid advance of industrialization and urbanization, the development and utilization of rivers and lakes and management and protection imbalance, excessive sewage, surrounding lakes and fields, encroachment of water and other disturbances highlight, resulting in black and smelly water, excessive water quality, environmental mess, ecological degradation.
Now, Ningxia is promoting the restoration of water ecological diversity, and trying to restore the Yellow River water show the river Qing.
The water should be treated from the source.
In Yinchuan, Ningxia, the local approach of“standard improvement+pollution control+strict control”has been adopted. All industrial parks have achieved centralized treatment of sewage, all urban sewage treatment plants have achieved level A standard discharge, and the black and smelly water bodies in urban built-up areas have basically been eliminated, and the third batch of Chinese black and smelly water demonstration cities have been successfully declared.
In addition, Ningxia fully implemented the river and lake long system in 2017, and now has realized the full coverage of the five-level river and lake long system responsibility system in districts, cities, counties and villages, and river and lake long patrol has become the norm.
Gu Jincheng, 64, who lives in a village along the Yellow River, witnessed the change: "The water used to stink, and after rectification, the stink was gone.”
Gu Jincheng said that the ecological environment is good,his life is more comfortable, now he often and his family go to the Yellow River for a walk, feel the clear water and blue sky.
"Wetland Dream" by Shagu Xiang Collection”
Flying birds, green trees, plank roads, clear water...... Fan Zhongyan's”Shagu Xiangji " beauty in the Yellow River Wetland Park in Yinchuan, Ningxia has become a reality.
The Yellow River flows through Ningxia, forming a variety of wetlands such as river wetlands, lake wetlands and marsh wetlands along the way, which plays an important role in promoting the rational utilization of water resources and the ecological balance of water, and also becomes an important international migration channel for birds.
Since 2009, the relevant departments of Ningxia have invested about 3.45 billion yuan in wetland protection projects.At present, Yinchuan Wetland covers an area of 19,200 hectares, with a wetland protection rate of 78.5%, there are nearly 200 natural lakes and marshes, and there are five national wetland parks, one national urban wetland park, six wetland parks at the autonomous region level and eight municipal parks.
Lv Jinhu, deputy director of Yinchuan Wetland Protection Center, told reporters that wetland protection has increased biodiversity, which is particularly evident in birds.“The gull is an endangered bird, there are only more than 20,000 birds in the world, of which Yinchuan Wetland inhabits more than 2,000."”
At the same time, Ningxia has delineated a red line of 500 meters for the wetland protection area on both sides of the Yinchuan section of the Yellow River according to law, stipulating that no unit or individual may carry out development, construction and business operations within the scope of protection except for public welfare projects.
Zhao Shaoyong, deputy director of Yinchuan Water Conservancy Service Center, said that through pollution source control, comprehensive remediation of river and lake ecology and the construction of end wetlands, the water quality of nine major yellow drainage ditches in Ningxia has now reached 100% of the class IV standard,“now the water is clear, the fish are also swimming, the flowers are also blooming."”
