Since 2010, Yinchuan City began to face a persistent summer peak water shortage problem, nearly a decade of "water shortage pain" has become a summer painful experience for many high-floor residents,but in the major water sources in the limit of over-mining, urban underground has formed a large area of groundwater over-mining funnel area under the status quo, water shortage has become a problem plaguing Yinchuan City.
Thanks to the improvement of the water quality of the Yellow River, drinking purified Yellow River water has become a solution to the problem of drinking water of local residents.
Ding Ming, deputy director of Yinchuan Municipal Water Bureau, introduced that in order to improve the demand for water for urban and rural residents in Yinchuan, Ningxia timely launched the water supply project for urban and rural western line in Yinchuan Metropolitan area, replacing the original groundwater source with high-quality Yellow River water.
On December 29, 2019, the water supply project officially opened to the three districts of Yinchuan. In 2020, residents of Minning Town and Helan County also drank the Yellow River water. ”
Ding Ming said that the Yinchuan water conservancy department will consider the integration of regional rural drinking water and urban water supply transformation, " the next step, we will integrate the rural decentralized water supply points after all access to the Western line water supply project, is expected to basically realize the integration of urban and rural water supply in Yinchuan region by the end of this year."”
