On the one hand, we need to do a good job in the implementation of the policies already introduced in the early stage, further strengthen the policy publicity, pay attention to creating a better business environment; on the other hand, we also need to further stimulate consumer demand, enrich the supply of tourism accommodation services, innovative service methods and strengthen cooperation between the government and platform enterprises, and further increase policy guidance and support.
